    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5232562>
    dc:description "Figure 3. Pseudophacopteron spp. (A, B) P. cuniculus; (C, D) P. nothospondiadis. (A) Antennal segments 3–4; (B) apex of antennal segment 4 with multiple rhinaria; (C) antennal segments 4–5; (D) apex of antennal segment 5 with single rhinarium. Scale bars: 0.03 mm (A); 0.005 mm (B, D); 0.01 mm (C)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5232562/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

